name: GeoNetNZ
0:
”Alexa, ask geo net for earthquakes.”
”Alexa, ask geo net did the ground shake.”
”Alexa, ask geo net was that an earthquake.”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: geo net
des:
A great tool for Kiwi's and their families.
It enables Alexa to obtain earthquake information for New Zealand.
This is obtained using the API kindly provided by Geo Net NZ.

We acknowledge the New Zealand GeoNet project and its sponsors EQC, GNS Science and LINZ, for providing data/images used in this skill.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
